title: Putumayo presents: Samba & Bossa Nova (2002)
description:
A new generation reinterprets and redefines the classic ideas of samba and bossa nova.
 
This eclectic compilation shows the syncopated and seductive evolution of the African-derived Brazilian samba and its offspring, the bossa nova. It features a new-wave series of moods and grooves tailor-made for the 21st century.
 
Everything here is performed with a real feeling and shows that the bossa nova and the samba can still give us new musical surprises.



Various Artists
